sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the Russell 3000 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Chipotle Mexican Grill Inc (Symbol: CMG), where a total volume of 9,096 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 909,600 underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 46.4% of CMG's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 2.0 million shares.
Particularly high volume was seen for the $325 strike call option expiring March 09, 2018 , with 412 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 41,200 underlying shares of CMG.
